tafsir[12]{c,v,t}:
  20,114,"Alla Toowii O Senike O Mawnii, ko O Lam…óo On Mo woodani …óum Laamu kala huunde, On Mo Ka√Īum ko Goonga Daalol Makko ngol ko Goonga, O Toowii e ko sirkoo…ďe …ďen sifotoo Mo kon, wata a he√Īo -an Nulaa…óo- janngugol Alqur'aana ngol wonndunde e Jibriila ko adii nde timmata e maa…óa yottinngol nde, Maaku: ""Joomi …ďeydanam Ganndal faade e ko Anndin…óaa lam kon""."
  20,115,"Gom…óii Men wasiyinoke Aadama ko adii fii waasu-de √Īaamugol leggal ngal, Men ha…ói mo e …óum, Men …ďannginani mo battane mu'un, o yejjiti wasiya on o √Īaami leggal ngal, o mun√Īaaki gaayi maggal, Men yi'naali mo doole pellital e dow reenugol ko Men wasiyii mo kon e mu'un."
  20,116,"JaŇčto -an Nulaa…óo- tuma nde Men Daalannoo Malaa'ikaa…ďe …ďen: ""Sujjanee Aadama sujjannde hiwraango"". ∆Āe sujji …ďe fow ma…ď…ďe si wanaa Ibliisa -on wonndu…óo e ma…ď…ďe kono o jeyaaka e ma…ď…ďe- o salori sujjugol ngol mawnintinaare."
  20,117,"Men Daali: ""Ko an yo Aadama, pellet, Ibliisa ko o ga√Īo maa…óa ko o ga√Īo sonnaajo maa on kadi, wata o yaltinire dey an e sonnaajo maa on ka Aljanna …óoftagol mo e huunde ko o sonwosinta e mu'un, sakko an ronndito…óaa sa…óteendeeji …óin e metteefooji …óin""."
  20,118,"Pellet, no woodanmaa ka Alla nde O Okkoray maa ke nder Aljanna hara a weeletaake, o holtine kadi hara a holataa."
  20,119,"∆äum woni O yarne hara a …óom…óetaake, O …óuwe hara nguleende naange hawrataa e maa…óa."
  20,120,"Seytaane sonwonsini Aadama, o wi'ani mo: ""Hara yo mi tinndine e leggal kala √Īaamu…óo ngal o maa- yataa poomaa, ko woni, o heddoto ko o wuuru…óo luttinaa…óo, o laamoo kadi laamu jokkondirngu ngu ta∆īataa ngu lannataa?!"""
  20,121,"Aadama e Hawaa √Īaami leggal ngal …ďe ha…óanoo ngal √Īaamugol, tageeji ma…ď…ďe …óin fee√Īani …ďe …ďaawo nde …ói laatinoo suu…óaa…ói, …ďe naati e woocugol haako le…ó…óe Aljanna …óen, …ďe suu…óira ko, tageeji ma…ď…ďe …óin, Aadama lunndii Yamiroore Joomi makko nden nde tawnoo o …óotaaki Yamiroore Makko nden fii wo…ó…óitagol √Īaamugol leggal ngal, o yawti o yahi e ko daganaaki mo."
  20,122,"Refti Alla Su…ďii mo O Ja…ďi tuubuubuyee makko on, O hawrinndini mo e Peewal ngal."
  20,123,"Alla Daalani Aadama e Hawaa: ""Jippee ka Aljanna onon e Ibliisa, on ko o ga√Īo mo'on, onon kadi ko on ay…ďe makko, Si aroyii e mo'on immorde e Am …ďanngal fii Laawol Am ngol: kala e mo'on jokku…óo …ďanngal Laawol Am ngol o golliri ngol hara o selaali ngol; haray o majjataa gaayi Goonga kan, o malkisiroytaake kadi Lepte ka Laakara, ko woni, Alla naaday mo Aljanna."
  20,124,"Kala …óuurii…óo e jaŇčtaande Lam hara o ja…ďaali …óum, haray jaabinantaake mo, haray pellet, no woodani mo ngurndam …ďittu…óam ka aduna e ka barjakhu, Men soggoyay mo kadi faade ka Mofturu √Ďalnde Darngal waasaa…óo gii…óe e dalil."
  20,125,"Oo …óurnii…óo e jaŇčtagol ngol wi'i: ""Ko An yo Joomi, ko fii hon…óum immintinir…óaa mi hannde ko mi bun…óo, gom…óii hari mi laatike ka aduna yi'oowo""."
